Title: Relates to naming a section of route 8 in the village of Sidney the "Sidney Veteran's Memorial Parkway"
Summary: Names a section of route 8 between the Susquehanna River and interstate eighty-eight in the village of Sidney the "Sidney Veteran's Memorial Parkway".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to naming a section of route 8 in the village of Sidney the "Sidney Veteran's Memorial Parkway"
